title: Online share of retail trade in selected countries 2014 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 12 different Countrys on X-axis for 5 groups 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding Share of retail trade.
Out of all 5 groups, 2017 had the highest Share of retail trade in Country United Kingdom and 2014 had the lowest Share of retail trade in Country Switzerland.
In Country United Kingdom, 2014 had the maximum Share of retail trade and it saw the lowest in Country Switzerland out of all 12 Countrys.
Country United Kingdom and Switzerland had the biggest gap of 134.0 between the highest and lowest Share of retail trade found for 2014.
